text: East Moriches is a small community in Long Island, New York with a population of about 6,000 people. It is in the town of Brookhaven. It is near Center Moriches or Moriches. East Moriches is near where the TWA flight 800 disaster happened. == References == Category:Hamlets in New York (state) Category:Census-designated places in New York (state)
title: East Moriches, New York
